snippet.title: BATTLEGROUNDS FOR ALL | PUBG
snippet.description:
The only thing better than a Chicken Dinner, is a FREE Chicken Dinner with your friend. From January 12th, PUBG: BATTLEGROUNDS embarks on a new journey; Free-to-play! Invite your friends and assemble your own squad! Pre-register now @ https://pre-reg.pubg.com

Stay up to date with #PUBG :
👉Website: https://global.battlegrounds.pubg.com/
👉Twitter: https://twitter.com/pubg
👉Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/pubg_battlegrounds_global
👉Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/pubg.battlegrounds.global
